		desc_tw = '【拉帝亞斯專屬】拉帝亞斯在場時，每個回合開始前為全体單位回復目標20%生命值的血量',
		desc_en = '[Latios Exclusive] While Latios is present, at the start of each turn, restore 20% of the target\'s HP to all units.',
