		desc_tw = '【路卡利歐專屬】友方使用小技能時40%有概率觸發小技能；友方使用必殺技時有40%概率觸發必殺技',
		desc_en = '[Lucario Exclusive] There is a 40% chance to trigger a small skill when an ally uses a small skill; there is a 40% chance to trigger an ultimate skill when an ally uses an ultimate skill.',
